text: European Georgia (, evropuli sakartvelo) is a political party in Georgia. Founded in Tbilisi in January 2017, by former members of the United National Movement. Chairman of Party is Giga Bokeria. ==Election results== Election year votes % of overall votes 2017 local election 156 232 10.4 (3rd) 2018 presidential election 174 849 10.97 (3rd) 2020 parliamentary election 72 752 3.78 (3rd) 2021 local election 29 280 1.66 ==References== Category:2017 establishments in Asia Category:Political parties in Europe Category:Organizations based in Georgia (country)
title: European Georgia
